{"tid":2145133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以前上training果陣話故意唔執行制裁 員工都要罰錢+坐監","createTime":"2020-08-08T01:44:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T06:30:56.000Z","uid":13663,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0ce5b5aacb6c9be1fdd2df85d7a1ca05cd504d0b","tid":2145133,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T01:44:25.000Z","msg":"依家仲有冇呢樣野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3840f48a2e89a4ee13f8af6cbf572c009e544291","tid":2145133,"uid":13663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T01:49:23.000Z","msg":"渣打違反制裁或再面臨巨額罰款 港股直擊 國際財經 | 2018年8月29日   AAA<br />\n Image description<br />\n渣打集團(02888)可能因為違反制裁伊朗規定，再次面臨巨額罰款。<br />\n<br />\n外電報道，渣打代表其伊朗客戶通過美國秘密轉移數十億美元的資金，違反制裁規定，因而付出沉重的罰金。據知情人士表示，一項調查發現，有證據顯示該行的伊朗業務比其承認的更為廣泛。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">消息稱，美國的執法和監管機構已完成調查，當局現正權衡對渣打和個別員工實施刑事處罰，開出的罰單金額可能超過該行2012年支付的6.67億美元，最遲於今年底宣布決議。</span><br />\n<br />\n渣打發言人稱，該行會繼續全力配合調查，並正與美國當局持續進行討論。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a59de82ee3970829e204e9eea74666be9abe166","tid":2145133,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T01:53:12.000Z","msg":"乜o野training先?"},{"pid":"ac8871aec0f89235b96ecab84ccff9578daf0bb3","tid":2145133,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T02:11:38.000Z","msg":"？"},{"pid":"a5b5622fac16bddcb5cb1e7b8f4a29f091b208d2","tid":2145133,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T02:12:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5QFkYyS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5QFkYyS.png&h=bd4957ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來仲有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb9f9d6079fcd553eb6d4d999bd2959e45a672af","tid":2145133,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T06:25:30.0